annotationA: tRNA (guanine-N(7)-)-methyltransferase; Catalyzes the formation of N(7)-methylguanine at position 46 (m7G46) in tRNA; Belongs to the class I-like SAM-binding methyltransferase superfamily. TrmB family
annotationB: Pescadillo homolog; Required for maturation of ribosomal RNAs and formation of the large ribosomal subunit
